Text:
Hi  HDvideos, 

Can you pls upload "The Avengers in Hindi"....

HDvideos, since you add your release info and "[Hindi-Eng]" in the metadata, it ruins the title when you run the movie. It's a pain to edit because they're .mkv files. Do us a favor and either switch file types or stop writing all that stuff in the title. Thanks anyway but I'm gonna download elsewhere.
